            <title><![CDATA[Ubisoft Doubles Down On Open-World And Live-Service Games]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/ubisoft-doubles-down-on-open-world-and-live-service-games/1100-6529497/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
